April 2008 (Ben Weiner) Rollout version 1.0 second release
- Incorporation of the OFL license
- Re-encoding font source files as FontForge ASCII text from MacroMedia Fontographer PostScript files

April 2001 (Ben Weiner) Rollout version 1.0
- Initial release of font "Rollout"

